<description>A skilful, attacking midfielder, Czech international Patrik came to Liverpool from Borussia Dortmund having helped them to win the Bundesliga.
Patrik was sadly plagued by injuries and required surgery, undermining his efforts but nevertheless scored some great goals before moving on in the summer of 2003.
His contract at Aston Villa was extended to June 2008 in May 2007.</description>

